    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="platform-chooser">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="chooser-grid">

        <a href="/guide/install-mac" class="platform-card">
          <div class="platform-icon">üçé</div>
          <h2>macOS</h2>
          <div class="platform-version">For MacBook or iMac users</div>
          <p>The easiest installation option ‚Äî perfect if you're on a Mac. Get up and running in under 10 minutes.</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Simplest setup of all options</li>
