          <div class="platform-version">For Windows PC users</div>
          <p>Perfect for Windows users. Needs one extra small step (about 10 minutes) to set up a Linux environment, then you're good to go.</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Works on Windows 10 and 11</li>
            <li>Setup is automatic ‚Äî just follow the guide</li>
            <li>Won't affect your existing files or programs</li>
          </ul>
          <div class="platform-cta">
            Windows Install Guide <span class="arrow">‚Üí</span>
          </div>
        </a>

        <a href="/guide/install-vps" class="platform-card recommended">
